    Class Description
    BlankLoginVerificationTest
    Test case to verify error messages displayed when user logs in without any user name and/or password
    BookHotel_BlankFields
    Test case to verify hotel booking without any input
    BookHotelVerificationTest
    Test case to verify if a user can book a hotel successfully with the details present in the Testdata file
    BookingCancelationVerification
    Test case to verify if the user can cancel a hotel booking.
    ForgotPasswordVerification
    Test case for forgot password verification
    InvalidLoginVerificationTest
    Test case to check if a user can login to the application with invalid user id and password It validates the error message which pops up
    LogoutVerification
    Test case to verify if user can logout successfully.
    ResetSearchVerification
    Test case to verify reset hotel in search hotel page

    Test case to verify searching for hotels with all inputs provided
    SearchHotel_BlankFields
    Test case to validate error alert when no input is provided while Searching Hotel
    SearchHotel_Location
    Test case to verify if user can search for hotel with location alone as the input Here each of the hotel entry in the list is verified for hotel name
    SearchHotel_LocationHotelName
    Test case to verify if the user can search for hotel with location and hotel name provided as input Each of the hotel entry displayed is verified for different room types
    SelectHotelVerification
    Test script to validate Select Hotel

    ViewItineraryVerification
